      "name": "OIDC Redirect URI",
      "description": "Full OIDC redirect/callback URL the application sends to Zitadel and that Zitadel registers as the only valid redirectUri for this client. Apps inherit a default from oci-image (https://{{hostname}}{{project_domain_suffix}}/api/auth/callback) and can override per app.",
