      "name": "OIDC Post-Logout URI",
      "description": "Full OIDC post-logout URL the application uses after sign-out and that Zitadel registers as the only valid postLogoutRedirectUri. Optional — when omitted, the OIDC app is created without a post-logout redirect, which is preferable when the landing page is itself OIDC-protected (Zitadel would otherwise loop the user back into the auth flow on logout).",
